text = "Movemens
______________________________


Objective: Survive as long as you can and kill as many
mobs as you can
WASD to move around
LMB to attack in the direction your mouse is facing
F to pick up a dropped weapon

Health is displayed top left
Current weapon is displayed bottom left
Minimap is displayed bottom right
Score and time survived are displayed top right"
percent_visible = 0.0

