custom_fonts/normal_font = SubResource( 7 )
text = "								Movements
					Move:						WASD
					Attack:					  RMB
					Roll:						 Space
					Pick up items:		 	F
					End game:				 Esc

		Aim:
		Survive as long as you can
		and kill as many monsters as you can
		
		Be aware! Weapons break easily!
		
		Tips:
			A mob has a chance to drop weapons upon death.
			Backstabbing a mob deals additional damage.
			There are special weapons hidden in the world."

